## Core User Flow

```
1. SELECT
   User selects clips on timeline (or entire sequence)
                    ↓
2. CONFIGURE (Optional)
   - Enable "Vocal Isolation" if audio has background noise
   - Choose output mode: Analysis Only | Replace | Both Tracks
                    ↓
3. LAUNCH
   Opens plugin panel → Clicks "Analyze Takes"
                    ↓
4. UPLOAD & PROCESS (Cloud)
   - Audio extracted and sent to cloud
   - Progress steps:
     ┌────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
     │ 1. ✓ Uploading audio                           │
     │ 2. → Isolating vocals... (if enabled)          │
     │ 3. ○ Transcribing speech                       │
     │ 4. ○ Analyzing takes                           │
     │ 5. ○ Preparing results                         │
     └────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
   - Without isolation: 30-90 seconds for 10-min footage
   - With isolation: ~7 minutes for 10-min footage
                    ↓
5. RESULTS APPEAR
   Timeline transforms:
   ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
   │ [■ Green] Take 1 - "Hey guys welcome back"      │
   │ [■ Green] Take 2 - "Hey guys welcome back" ★    │
   │ [■ Blue]  Take 1 - "So today I want to show"    │
   │ [■ Blue]  Take 2 - "So today I want to show" ★  │
   │ [■ Blue]  Take 3 - "So today I wan-" (partial)  │
   └─────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

   Panel shows:
   - "Found 12 unique lines across 31 takes"
   - "Detected 4m 20s of removable silence"
   - "3 incomplete takes flagged"

   If Vocal Isolation was enabled (Replace or Both Tracks):
   - Isolated audio track imported to project
   - Applied based on user's output mode selection
                    ↓
6. REVIEW & ADJUST
   - Click any take group to expand/collapse
   - Preview takes with spacebar
   - Override AI's "best" pick if desired
   - Uncheck takes to keep (won't be deleted)
   - Toggle between original/isolated audio (if Both Tracks)
                    ↓
7. EXECUTE
   Three options:
   [Keep Best Takes Only] - Deletes all but starred
   [Remove Silences Only] - Keeps all takes, trims gaps
   [Full Cleanup] - Both actions
                    ↓
8. DONE
   "Removed 8m 32s | Kept 12 best takes | Timeline ready"
   Full undo available
```

---

## Technical Architecture

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    PREMIERE PRO (UXP)                       │
│  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────────────┐  │
│  │ Plugin UI   │  │ Timeline    │  │ Audio Extraction    │  │
│  │ (React/JS)  │  │ Manipulation│  │ (temp WAV export)   │  │
│  └──────┬──────┘  └──────┬──────┘  └──────────┬──────────┘  │
└─────────┼────────────────┼────────────────────┼─────────────┘
          │                │                    │
          ▼                ▼                    ▼
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                      SPLICE CLOUD API                       │
│  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────────────┐  │
│  │ Auth/Billing│  │ Job Queue   │  │ Storage (temp audio)│  │
│  │ - Tier check│  │ - Priority  │  │ - Original audio    │  │
│  │   for vocal │  │   routing   │  │ - Isolated vocals   │  │
│  │   isolation │  │             │  │   (if requested)    │  │
│  └─────────────┘  └──────┬──────┘  └─────────────────────┘  │
│                          │                                   │
│    ┌─────────────────────┼─────────────────────┐            │
│    │ (if vocal isolation enabled)              │            │
│    ▼                                           │            │
│  ┌─────────────────────┐                       │            │
│  │ DEMUCS              │                       │            │
│  │ (GPU Workers)       │                       │            │
│  │ - htdemucs model    │                       │            │
│  │ - T4/A10 GPUs       │                       │            │
│  │ - Auto-scaling      │                       │            │
│  └──────────┬──────────┘                       │            │
│             │                                  │            │
│             ▼                                  ▼            │
│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐    │
│  │                  PROCESSING PIPELINE                │    │
│  │                                                     │    │
│  │  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌────────────┐   │    │
│  │  │ Transcribe  │→ │ LLM Analysis│→ │ Results    │   │    │
│  │  │ (Whisper)   │  │ (GPT-4o-mini│  │ Formatter  │   │    │
│  │  │             │  │             │  │ (JSON)     │   │    │
│  │  └─────────────┘  └─────────────┘  └────────────┘   │    │
│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘    │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Demucs GPU Infrastructure
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                   GPU WORKER POOL (Auto-scaling)            │
│                                                             │
│  ┌───────────┐  ┌───────────┐  ┌───────────┐  ┌─────────┐   │
│  │ Worker 1  │  │ Worker 2  │  │ Worker 3  │  │Worker N │   │
│  │ (T4 GPU)  │  │ (T4 GPU)  │  │ (T4 GPU)  │  │(T4 GPU) │   │
│  │ htdemucs  │  │ htdemucs  │  │ htdemucs  │  │htdemucs │   │
│  └───────────┘  └───────────┘  └───────────┘  └─────────┘   │
│                                                             │
│  Scaling Rules:                                             │
│  - Min: 1 worker (always warm)                              │
│  - Max: 10 workers (based on queue depth)                   │
│  - Pro tier jobs get priority routing                       │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

---

## Infrastructure Cost Analysis

### Vocal Isolation (Demucs) Costs

#### GPU Worker Costs (AWS G4dn.xlarge - NVIDIA T4)

| Scenario | Workers | Hours/Month | Cost/Hour | Monthly Cost |
|----------|---------|-------------|-----------|--------------|
| Minimum (always-on) | 1 | 720 | $0.526 | $379 |
| Average load | 3 | 720 | $0.526 | $1,137 |
| Peak periods | 10 | 200 | $0.526 | $1,052 |
| **Total estimated** | — | — | — | **$2,500-3,500** |

#### Cost Per Processing Minute

| Audio Length | Demucs GPU Time | GPU Cost | Storage Cost | Total Cost |
|--------------|-----------------|----------|--------------|------------|
| 1 minute | 40 seconds | $0.006 | $0.001 | ~$0.007 |
| 10 minutes | 6 minutes | $0.053 | $0.005 | ~$0.058 |
| 60 minutes | 36 minutes | $0.316 | $0.025 | ~$0.34 |

#### Break-Even Analysis by Tier

| Tier | Price | Vocal Isolation Users (est.) | Avg Minutes/Month | Cost to SPLICE | Margin Impact |
|------|-------|------------------------------|-------------------|----------------|---------------|
| Creator | $34.99 | 30% | 150 min | $1.05 | -3.0% |
| Pro | $69.99 | 50% | 400 min | $2.36 | -3.4% |

**Conclusion:** Vocal isolation cost is easily absorbed within existing tier pricing. No price adjustment needed.

### Self-Hosted vs. Third-Party API

| Factor | Self-Hosted Demucs | Third-Party API |
|--------|--------------------|-----------------|
| Per-minute cost | ~$0.007 | $0.05-0.15 (estimated) |
| Setup complexity | High | Low |
| Maintenance | Required | None |
| Latency | Optimizable | Variable |
| Scaling | Manual/auto | Automatic |
| **Recommendation** | **Yes** | No |

**Result:** Self-hosting is 10-20x cheaper at scale and provides better control.

